original_title: Just For Laughs: Working Class Comics
overview: Live from Just For Laughs, the Montreal International Comedy Festival, come the funniest comics to ever take the stage at the world's largest and most prestigious comedy event! With hilarious performances by: Larry the Cable Guy, Ron White, Frank Caliendo, Jeff Foxworthy, Bill Engvall, Jon Reep, Dom Irrera, John Caparulo, John Caponera, Kathleen Madigan, Joe Starr, Michael Loftus, Rocky Laporte, and Steve McGrew.
title: Just For Laughs: Working Class Comics
